<F P=106> [CTK report: "Drugs at the Borders and at Ruzyne Airport as </F>
Well"] 
  [Text] Prague--Folmava customs seized over 30 kg of heroin 
worth 55 million korunas [Kc] from a Turkish truck yesterday. 
The hiding place was professionally manufactured in the brake 
cylinders and perfectly disguised. The screws were covered with 
putty, and the hiding place was sprayed with paint. 
  On Tuesday [12 April] at Ruzyne Airport, customs officers 
discovered more than 1.5 kg of cocaine, worth almost Kc5.5 
million, in the false bottom of a a Dutch citizen's suitcase. 

